desc: Q: Do I have to bring Photo ID? A: No, unless you do not have a copy of your ticket Q: Is there an age requirement? A: Children under the age of 10 are required to be accompanied by an adult. Q: When should I arrive? What if I am late? A: Check-in is two hours before show starts. Audience load in one hour before show starts. No worries if you are late there will always be someone available to check you in.? Q: How is seating arranged? A: There is bleacher seating inside and outside on a first come, first serve basis.
